Interface BatchAIJob.DefinitionStages.WithEnvironmentVariableSecretValue

        value - value of the variable to set
        Returns:

      • withEnvironmentVariableSecretValue

        BatchAIJob.DefinitionStages.WithCreate withEnvironmentVariableSecretValue(String name,
                                                                          String keyVaultId,

        Specifies KeyVault Store and Secret which contains the value for the environment variable.
        Parameters:
        name - name of the variable to set
        keyVaultId - fully qualified resource Id for the Key Vault
        secretUrl - the URL referencing a secret in a Key Vault
        Returns:
        the next stage of the definition
